    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Build your empire:</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Build up new cities with strong economies to keep citizens happy</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >and military resolve to keep them safe from invading forces.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219250/extras/522df743d589cd7e23bf66f5bbd58636.poster.avif?t=1750928212\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219250/extras/522df743d589cd7e23bf66f5bbd58636.webm?t=1750928212\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219250/extras/522df743d589cd7e23bf66f5bbd58636.mp4?t=1750928212\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Find new races across Avandalair:</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >From friendly settlements willing to trade and work together,<br>to settlements ruled by warlords, beast races or world conquering hiveminds.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Will you wage war or make alliances?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219250/extras/0fab1ad120e83bbc6e710ae879360fa9.poster.avif?t=1750928212\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219250/extras/0fab1ad120e83bbc6e710ae879360fa9.webm?t=1750928212\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219250/extras/0fab1ad120e83bbc6e710ae879360fa9.mp4?t=1750928212\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Explore Avandalair's world: </strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Discover old world technology to unlock new weapons, upgrades and city improvements<strong>.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219250/extras/b3c9663a3c119ad0bf930c6586ed1753.poster.avif?t=1750928212\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219250/extras/b3c9663a3c119ad0bf930c6586ed1753.webm?t=1750928212\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219250/extras/b3c9663a3c119ad0bf930c6586ed1753.mp4?t=1750928212\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Key Features:</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Exploration</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-Discover new races, friend or foe.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-Discover new lands to populate with new settlements.</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Building</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-Build your cities in unique locations.<br>-Connect cities by trade routes and manage various things <br>  to keep the population happy.<br>-Raise defensive structures and armies to protect your cities.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Combat</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-Combat your enemies with various unique upgradable weapons.<br>-Raise armies to defend your cities and assault others.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-Use vehicles and tamable mounts on land, water and air to travel and fight.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-Fight epic bosses that will test your resolve.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Skill trees:</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-Unlock skills and abilities in unique skill trees.<br>-Upgrade weapons and equipment like the placeable turret.</p>",
